# Footer: references, breaking changes, etc.
#
# === EXAMPLES ===
# feat: add MCP server configuration validation
# fix(mcp-manager): resolve Docker image cleanup
# docs: update README with server addition protocol
# refactor: extract shared utility functions
# test: add integration tests for MCP servers
# chore: update dependencies to latest versions
#
# === BREAKING CHANGES ===
# feat!: restructure temporary directory organization
# BREAKING CHANGE: Temporary files now organized under ./tmp/
#
# === ANTI-PATTERNS TO AVOID ===
# ❌ feat: adding new feature (wrong tense)
# ❌ feat: add feature. (ends with period)
# ❌ Added feature (no type, past tense)
# ❌ Very long commit message that exceeds fifty characters (too long)
